 # tiếng Việt # Trịnh Tắc Sỹ, Huỳnh Quang Lượng, Trần Vỹ # TVB 2016","link_embed":"https://vip.opstream13.com/share/f7fbc4bafcc80cbf690acbef25f2ce1c","link_m3u8":"https://vip.opstream13.com/20250905/6289_f7fbc4ba/index.m3u8"}]}],"time":"45 phút/tập","description":"Ever since falling in love, former triad member Ho Keisong has put his former gang life behind to become a chef. Life is good as he and his wife make a good living at their small restaurant and their daughter works as an investment banker. But their happy family life is threatened when Keisong's former triad boss Lau Cheuknam is released from prison. Not only does Cheuknam wants to pull Keisong back into the triad life, but Keisong's marriage is also on the line as his wife was Cheuknam's girlfriend before his incarceration.","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"96689","season":1,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},"modified":"2025-09-07T18:01:51.000Z","cast":["Trịnh Tắc Sĩ","Huỳnh Quang Lượng","Trần Vỹ","Eliza Sam","Trần Sơn Thông","Mat Yeung","Uyển Quỳnh Đan","Jin Gang","La Lạc Lâm","Lý Thành Xương","Ada Wong Chi-Hom"],"director":[],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Trịnh Tắc Sĩ","name_vi":"Trịnh Tắc Sĩ","name_original":"Kent Cheng Jak-Si","tmdb_id":65966,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/a1ebM3aLwYkPckPzc9FgfW2xTsZ.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/65966"},{"name":"Huỳnh Quang Lượng","name_vi":"Huỳnh Quang Lượng","name_original":"Tommy Wong","tmdb_id":1135394,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4vcp6AtQpaW5LrAwkDudVy6ibUt.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1135394"},{"name":"Trần Vỹ","name_vi":"Trần Vỹ","name_original":"Alice Chan Wai","tmdb_id":1021936,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wxRBCvpATXZ5y4ejR7JrSChmS3N.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1021936"},{"name":"Eliza Sam","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Eliza Sam","tmdb_id":1688880,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cBjklXUuITK69b75HaEVltOdwnC.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/perso